App much detail and conveniently control your daily income and expenses. For those who would like to save your budget carefully. We are happy to assist you!!
Quick Access Icons will help you to save your time. Just click on the desired category, and enter your expenses or income, and the rest of the app will do for you!

Simple, but at the same time user-friendly interface. Our goal in the design of the application is not brilliance and convenience. We have tried to do everything so that the interface was clear to all, without exception.
You can synchronize data using your Google account. On all devices, you can recover your data! The data is stored in a very secure Google servers.

The application will show the statistics of your expenses and income. You will be able to predict costs. A full report on all the information in an understandable way, with the ability to save in EXCEL.

To synchronize data, you must log in with your Google Account. You can download from any device, anywhere. You can restore all the lost data! To restore the data, go to Settings-> Google Sync-> Download Database.
If you are synchronized, your data will be overwritten.
